<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hinkhuo phat sung a chawm hi,
 Thingnah pulh zel bang ahi;
 Buhphal kankhawm bang ahi, Kisau in!
 Ni bei zel hin ei hilh hi;
 Thihna hungtung pai ding chuh,
 Damlai sunni tum ina, Kisau in!

[V2]
 Kisau in; Kisau in!
 Isu Awn A hun sap lai hin, Kisau in!
 Gilo a na um zing chun,
 Hinna kawt hawn mu puon la,
 Nang di'n hun kikhel ina; Kisau in!

[V3]
 2. Pakcha hawihpen a vuoi pai,
 Hat lai, hawih lai a hung bei;
 Aw hun sawt na neita puou,
 Kisau in!
 Thagau thieng hun chiel lai hin,
 Mi gilo vakmang ta ki'n;
 Manthaina chuh tuok khan lau,
 Kisau in!

[V4]
 3. Phat kintak in a bei zel,
 Thihna, vaihawmna anai;
 Isu ban chu hun bel un,
 Kisau in!
 A lulzie chuh ngaihtuoh in,
 A phat a kikhelh mahin,
 Na thau gawtmun a tun ma'n,
 Kisau in!

[V5]
 4. Gilo, hilhna Aw ngai in,
 Lalpa chuh hun pawm inla;
 Van mipi kipak unau,
 Kisau in!
 Thim apat vak ah hung un,
 Isun hun na siemphan a;
 Van zuon di'n tun kipan un,
 Kisau in!</lyrics>
<title>LIFE AT BEST IS VERY BRIEF</title>
<hymn_number>238</hymn_number>
</song>